snippet.title: Cory in the Ded 3.5 - SAGE 2023 Demo Release
snippet.description:
https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/cory-in-the-ded-3-5-sage-23-demo.1622/

Trailer created by @ABlob , thank you so much for coming in clutch and creating this wonderful trailer for me!
Credit also goes to @KwasiorRandom  for the Reach for the Stars (Recolors) instrumental A Blob used.

------------------

Cory in the Ded 3.5's new demo will be arriving September 1st, 2023, aka TODAY! Join Radfordhound & The Resistance on an multiversial journey, fully updated for a new expo -- with a few new features, too! Available RIGHT NOW!

https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/cory-in-the-ded-3-5-sage-23-demo.1622/

Cory in the Ded 3.5 is being developed by BriceTAS, a passionate guy known for his weird games.
